```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''haptic'''
|^a pointer to the^ haptic device to ,,get the index of,, ^query^
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the index of the ^specified^ haptic device or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

